d"},{"id":15645,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱعْمَلُوٓا۟","translation":"\"(আরও বলেছিলাম) তোমরা কাজ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15646,"position":13,"arabic":"ءَالَ","translation":"(হে)বংশধররা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15647,"position":14,"arabic":"دَاوُۥدَ","translation":"দাউদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15648,"position":15,"arabic":"شُكْرًۭا ۚ","translation":"কৃতজ্ঞতা সহকারে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15650,"position":16,"arabic":"وَقَلِيلٌۭ","translation":"এবং কমই","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15651,"position":17,"arabic":"مِّنْ","translation":"মধ্যে হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15652,"position":18,"arabic":"عِبَادِىَ","translation":"আমার দাসদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15653,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلشَّكُورُ","translation":"কৃতজ্ঞ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_013_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15654,"position":20,"arabic":"١٣","translation":"(১৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":14,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا قَضَيْنَا عَلَيْهِ ٱلْمَوْتَ مَا دَلَّهُمْ عَلَىٰ مَوْتِهِۦٓ إِلَّا دَآبَّةُ ٱلْأَرْضِ تَأْكُلُ مِنسَأَتَهُۥ ۖ فَلَمَّا خَرَّ تَبَيَّنَتِ ٱلْجِنُّ أَن لَّوْ كَانُوا۟ يَعْلَمُونَ ٱلْغَيْبَ مَا لَبِثُوا۟ فِى ٱلْعَذَابِ ٱلْمُهِينِ","translation":"Yet [even Solomon had to die; but] when We decreed that he should die, nothing showed them that he was dead except an earthworm that gnawed away his staff. And when he fell to the ground, those invisible beings [subservient to him] saw clearly that, had they but understood the reality which was be­yond the reach of their perception, they would not have continued [to toil] in the shameful suffering [of servitude]","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3620.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":16674,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","trans